title: Shaq, Kenny, Chuck and Ernie React to the Finalists for NBA Awards | NBA on TNT
author: NBA on TNT
description:
The Inside crew discusses the finalists named for the Rookie of the Year, Coach of the Year, Sixth Man of the Year, Defensive Player of the Year and Most Improved Player. 

Watch highlights from Inside the NBA with Shaq, Charles Barkley, Kenny Smith and Ernie Johnson and more! Subscribe now to be updated on the latest videos: https://www.youtube.com/nbaontnt?sub_confirmation=1
